       a UNIX or Linux account on a machine somewhere. (a shell account  
       with an editor like VI.) Once you complete what you feel is a good 
       job post a note on the Admin Board in room 1201 for promotion. The 30 
       days here is not required.

LEVEL - 60
----------

        Welcome to the coder and upper admin levels. These levels are 
